 helping diagnose cases where builds may not be updated.\n\nResolves feedback from PR #260\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>","tree":{"sha":"dc9c3955d9319ddbc83d981e11bf1cd41306a1a0","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/git/trees/dc9c3955d9319ddbc83d981e11bf1cd41306a1a0"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/git/commits/3288d5a958f4349f85b8137666847cfe9b2da91b","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":false,"reason":"unsigned","signature":null,"payload":null,"verified_at":null}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commits/3288d5a958f4349f85b8137666847cfe9b2da91b","html_url":"https://github.com/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commit/3288d5a958f4349f85b8137666847cfe9b2da91b","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commits/3288d5a958f4349f85b8137666847cfe9b2da91b/comments","author":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"parents":[{"sha":"0df23ecb6626a3c684d474f2a0e113843b89feef","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commits/0df23ecb6626a3c684d474f2a0e113843b89feef","html_url":"https://github.com/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commit/0df23ecb6626a3c684d474f2a0e113843b89feef"}]},{"sha":"ccc03e6b0f1826f03f9ec856edac69d9529cc182","node_id":"C_kwDOQ35I0doAKGNjYzAzZTZiMGYxODI2ZjAzZjllYzg1NmVkYWM2OWQ5NTI5Y2MxODI","commit":{"author":{"name":"konard","email":"drakonard@gmail.com","date":"2026-01-22T20:21:02Z"},"committer":{"name":"konard","email":"drakonard@gmail.com","date":"2026-01-22T20:21:02Z"},"message":"Implement velocity-based grenade throwing in Player.cs (C#)\n\nRoot cause: The C# Player.cs was still using legacy drag-based throwing\nwhile only the GDScript player.gd was updated. The game uses the C# code\npath, so velocity-based physics were never applied.\n\nChanges to Scripts/Characters/Player.cs:\n- Add mouse velocity tracking with 5-sample history for smooth velocity\n- Add total swing distance tracking for momentum transfer calculation\n- Update ThrowGrenade() to use throw_grenade_velocity_based() method\n- Update UpdateWindUpIntensity() for velocity-based wind-up animation\n- Update debug trajectory visualization for velocity-based predictions\n- Add startup log showing which throwing system is active\n\nKey behavior change:\n- Mouse VELOCITY at release determines throw power (not drag distance)\n- If mouse is stopped at release, grenade drops at player's feet\n- Faster mouse movement = farther throw\n- Swing distance affects momentum transfer efficiency\n\nThis syncs the C# implementation with the GDScript velocity-based system.\n\nResolves issue #256 feedback: \"even if mouse is completely stopped,\ngrenade still flies far (should stay in place)\"\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>","tree":{"sha":"9ac479663adcdf9b3a0a26f692c1a9943abcdd6b","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/git/trees/9ac479663adcdf9b3a0a26f692c1a9943abcdd6b"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/git/commits/ccc03e6b0f1826f03f9ec856edac69d9529cc182","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":false,"reason":"unsigned","signature":null,"payload":null,"verified_at":null}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commits/ccc03e6b0f1826f03f9ec856edac69d9529cc182","html_url":"https://github.com/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commit/ccc03e6b0f1826f03f9ec856edac69d9529cc182","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/Jhon-Crow/godot-topdown-MVP/commits/ccc03e6b0f1826f03f9ec856edac69d9529cc182/comments","author":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"ht